PrecisAppointment of CLARENCE LeBRETON, of Caraquet, New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Broadcasting Corporation to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, in the place of Nancy L. Juneau, whose term has expired.
